Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are eating, so don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to see it with your own eyes than to hear about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka is finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you girls screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Valentine's is nearly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt these festive youngsters will listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Valentine's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pretending! Those lies won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:36.32,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to make out while I'm not paying attention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing such indecent things at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's really pointless to give or receive chocolate at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School is a place to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're being lectured by Haruta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's school for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Health care and PE, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Aisaka-san, please come to the interview room after school.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.17,0:01:11.96,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fs48\pos(363.636364,520.5)}The Road We Must Advance on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you still can't turn in your career assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Aisaka-san, you haven't even turned the one from the first semester in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm still discussing it with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother wants you to go to college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko has{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother has always been a hard worker, but sometimes she pushes herself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a burden anymore, so I'm not planning on going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aisaka-san, what's your reason for not turning it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I come from a rich family, so I won't ever need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also why I don't need to study. Plus there's nothing I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't go to college{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. It's just that you'll be on your own for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just blame stuff on others. No one will take responsibility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you two to carefully think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you haven't gone against your mother's intentions, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:13.94,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz340\pos(566,254)\c&H4A638E&}Interview room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you've finished filling it out, bring it to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of my life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's the career assessment form{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for me to think about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even recognize myself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always denied my present self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is this happening?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What should I do to avoid it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I know what I want to do later when I don't even know what I want to do right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fall in love normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't even have someone{\fscx301.8868}-{\fscx100.62893} no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I like? I don't even know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be born into a normal family, then raised as a normal good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then have a normal encounter with a guy and become friends normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fall in love normally like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you using past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the conditions are already wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not normal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's right and what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there to decide on those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, why are you suddenly lecturing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the career assessments?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home. I don't give a damn about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.09,Plain,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(800,0)\frz11\pos(610,248)\c&H464A72&}I wish to find a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I already refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kawashima, think about it one more{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to think about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kawashima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do to my shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a shoe fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to set a record for long throws at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you called to the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn't model the school uniform for a school information pamphlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you refuse? Isn't that your speciality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how much longer I'll be at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that your fight with Kushieda{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a trivial person like Kushieda Minori couldn't have an influence on my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I planned to leave after the first semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News about the stalker thing has died down too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard you mention{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I wanted to stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with you guys tomorrow, or even the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched Taiga get hurt and understood her pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that since I understood her, I'd save her if no one else did, or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I realize that everything would sort itself out if I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now of all{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga? I'm really bu{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My part-time job at the cake store too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even made a cute uniform for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted both places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest and don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaa-chan is sleeping, shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, how's Yaa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god, seeing her faint from my window scared the heck out of{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy something for Yasuko to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ryuuji! What about your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left your cell phone, wallet, and key! Your eco-bag too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, put it on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, why are you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm all right! You wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're acting all weird now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuj{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko fainted because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has anemia! It's her body! It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.65,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't that useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko would have more faith and trust in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would rely on me more... then things like this would never happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Everything's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everything's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's all right, I'm a superb mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow and the day after tomorrow are the busiest times because of Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, she really can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to find a substitute at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.70,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something for Yaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fired from my part-time job at the cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll be able to find another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you comforting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it with a stronger voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, your face wasn't born for advertising food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are really working!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun, which one do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you buy big ones, bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take that big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have this one, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That'll be 580 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my sister, she's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, have fun with your jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a warm place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:22.36,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world really has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noto! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just happened to pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, has anyone else come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, Ami-chan, or even Nanako-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No! I don't really care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if Kihara will give Kitamura chocolate or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look, Taiga, you care about "that," don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean by "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why does Kihara Maya buying chocolate for Kitamura-kun concern you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. You like Kihara Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So people who realize their feelings after fighting really do exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.45,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.91,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so strange, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's strange at all. It's perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A male's stamen and a female's pistil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be scolded if we mess around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no other choice than to summon the lethal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, stupid chi-, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. Don't make me do weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beautiful, so I naturally grab people's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, you're beautiful! You're really attractive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should take this and say "I love the chocolate here!" out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to advertise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do such a lame thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, stupid chi-.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, how about you buy one for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could give it to Minorin to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary to popular belief, I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get on good terms with Minorin, but it's not working out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shaking delicate heart of a chihuahua{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you making assump{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're embarrassed, I'll call Minorin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, Valentine's Day came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Kawashima Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her face is so slender!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she buying chocolate at that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the chocolate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my model friends say it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy the same kind as Ami-chan's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she can be helpful from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, where are you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I would like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like chasing after people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have potential to be a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, you like running away, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just from me, but from a lot of other things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I don't think it'd be better if you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you'll disappoint everyone if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone adores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Taiga can't handle it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'd be happy even if it wasn't everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it myself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll be counting on you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached our target already, so it was pointless to buy the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I'm going to give them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I caused a lot of trouble for people on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kitamura-kun, and Minorin, and the stupid chi-.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I gave you chocolate, would you be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be human if getting chocolate from you didn't make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just giving you guys store-bought chocolate is rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll try to do something nice with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully I can make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the shop already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all healthy now, so it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to thank Taiga-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring us all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Valentine's Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I made some chocolate to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be such a waste to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the chocolate you were selling yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at telling lies{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wrapping was nice so I reused it, but I made everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't help you with stuff like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Minorin's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you went to save me during the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be so formal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to save you whenever you're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you too, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Share it with Yaa-chan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Kitamura-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put the most effort into this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you were the person who carried me from the bottom of the cliff, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I didn't tell Kushieda to{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my eyes were all white...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't expect that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rolled down like this, and there were some weird noises in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found out what fainting feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I blurted out things that I wasn't supposed to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I regained my consciousness, I started to panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you blurted out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it! I really can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I can't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! Anyway, it was just my delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that no one should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be ruined if people find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to live anymore because it's something really, really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard nothing, right, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one heard anything, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think everything will be all right if you pretend you didn't hear it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing, Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you're glad that no one heard it because that solves everything, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun was the one who saved you, but he just didn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't tell you because of what you said, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why can't you just be honest for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you look scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid chi-...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'll be all right if you let Aisaka run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.21,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see me as?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.22,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minorin, your best friend, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.64,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're the kind of person to blame others for your inability to go after what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you someone like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want the Minorin I love to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness can only be.... can only be made with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness doesn't depend on anyone but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, are you betraying us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad things will happen if you don't chase after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, I'll chase after Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking with her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if I chase after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I do after I find out how Taiga feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She obviously wanted to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
