Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:49.73,Ep Titles 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\pos(1061.818182,547.5)}Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga, it's about to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The laundry is still outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I left a lot of things out.
